    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, reduce the heat to medium-high, then add your<strong> creamy sauce</strong> and <strong>blanched peas</strong> to the pan, give everything a good mix up and bring to the boil</p><p>Cook for 30 secs, or until the sauce has slightly thickened, then add your <strong>drained tortelloni </strong>to the pan with a splash of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and cook for a final 30 secs or until the sauce is coating the pasta – this is your <strong>creamy bacon & pea sauce with mushroom tortelloni</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
