    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy bacon & pea sauce with mushroom tortelloni</strong> topped with the<strong> remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and <strong>chopped basil</strong></p><p>Drizzle with <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
